<B>__{another angle}
<A>__{stump stops his car and gets out he hurries to the edge of the road where the bank drops away quickly. pov shot cobb's car lies nose down at the bottom of a snow filled ravine, thirty feet away. the tail lights are still on. the car is totalled.}
